---


<div class="flex flex-col h-full justify-center space-y-5">
    <div class="laptop:max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-center">
        <h3 class="font-blackstone tablet:text-center tablet:text-size-8 laptop:text-size-11 text-light-rose text-center text-[3rem] font-light opacity-0" :class="intersect ? 'animate-fade-up animate-ease-in-out  animate-delay-200 ' : 'opacity-0'">Contact Me</h3>
        <h4 class="font-prata text-size-6  text-left ">Book a free discovery call by clicking the button below to our email!</h4>
        <p class="font-tajawal tablet:text-left text-justify text-[20px] text-[#515151]">Whether you have a question about the services, pricing, or anything else, I'm ready to answer any questions you might have. Click the button to send me an email and I promise to get back to you as soon as I can.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tablet:justify-center flex w-full justify-center gap-5">
        <CalendlyWidget />
       
    </div>
</div>